{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Ipoool's Blog","author":"Asep Saepulloh"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"7dc6de12-ed49-57be-88c5-786885510d42","excerpt":"Hari ini gue mau  share  sedikit tentang cara membuat Github Pages Untuk yang mau tau apa itu Github Pages, Silakan baca  disini . Oke, kita…","html":"<p>Hari ini gue mau <em>share</em> sedikit tentang cara membuat Github Pages</p>\n<p>Untuk yang mau tau apa itu Github Pages, Silakan baca <a href=\"https://help.github.com/articles/what-is-github-pages/\" title=\"What is Github Pages\">disini</a>.</p>\n<p>Oke, kita langsung aja :</p>\n<p>Buat temen-temen yang belum memiliki akun Github. Silakan <em>register</em> terlebih dahulu <a href=\"https://github.com/join?source=login\" title=\"Register Github Account\">disini</a>, tetapi jika temen-temen sudah punya. Kita bisa lanjut ke tahap selanjutnya.</p>\n<p>Temen-temen bisa membuat <em>Repository</em> baru untuk menyimpan <em>file-file static</em> yang akan di generate pada github pages nanti. </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/github-page-create-a-repository-3b360041a3de7aa283513507beababc2-1f4df.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.47619047619048%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Create a new Repository\"\n        title=\"Create a new Repository\"\n        src=\"/static/github-page-create-a-repository-3b360041a3de7aa283513507beababc2-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/github-page-create-a-repository-3b360041a3de7aa283513507beababc2-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/github-page-create-a-repository-3b360041a3de7aa283513507beababc2-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/github-page-create-a-repository-3b360041a3de7aa283513507beababc2-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/github-page-create-a-repository-3b360041a3de7aa283513507beababc2-1f4df.png 840w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Disini gue buat <em>repository</em> dengan nama “my-github-page”, setelah itu kita <em>submit</em></p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/github-page-setting-menu-77d8877ccfaaf88ad890fe9c9e0c6642-a90c2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 32.580961727183514%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Choose a Setting menu\"\n        title=\"Choose a Setting menu\"\n        src=\"/static/github-page-setting-menu-77d8877ccfaaf88ad890fe9c9e0c6642-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/github-page-setting-menu-77d8877ccfaaf88ad890fe9c9e0c6642-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/github-page-setting-menu-77d8877ccfaaf88ad890fe9c9e0c6642-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/github-page-setting-menu-77d8877ccfaaf88ad890fe9c9e0c6642-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/github-page-setting-menu-77d8877ccfaaf88ad890fe9c9e0c6642-526de.png 885w,\n/static/github-page-setting-menu-77d8877ccfaaf88ad890fe9c9e0c6642-a90c2.png 1019w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Setelah <em>repository</em> berhasil dibuat, selanjutnya kita pilih Menu <em>Setting</em></p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/github-page-theme-menu-517582d246db47ae203c1dee58a56ac7-85f04.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 49.673202614379086%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Choose a Theme menu\"\n        title=\"Choose a Theme menu\"\n        src=\"/static/github-page-theme-menu-517582d246db47ae203c1dee58a56ac7-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/github-page-theme-menu-517582d246db47ae203c1dee58a56ac7-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/github-page-theme-menu-517582d246db47ae203c1dee58a56ac7-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/github-page-theme-menu-517582d246db47ae203c1dee58a56ac7-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/github-page-theme-menu-517582d246db47ae203c1dee58a56ac7-85f04.png 765w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Cari bagian “Github Pages” pada menu <em>Setting</em>, pilih menu <em>Theme</em> untuk memilih desain yang kita inginkan</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/github-page-choose-a-theme-d1fcacdf1eba8b941cf78b042211a661-d465c.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 56.25570776255707%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Select the Theme\"\n        title=\"Select the Theme\"\n        src=\"/static/github-page-choose-a-theme-d1fcacdf1eba8b941cf78b042211a661-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/github-page-choose-a-theme-d1fcacdf1eba8b941cf78b042211a661-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/github-page-choose-a-theme-d1fcacdf1eba8b941cf78b042211a661-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/github-page-choose-a-theme-d1fcacdf1eba8b941cf78b042211a661-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/github-page-choose-a-theme-d1fcacdf1eba8b941cf78b042211a661-526de.png 885w,\n/static/github-page-choose-a-theme-d1fcacdf1eba8b941cf78b042211a661-d465c.png 1095w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Pilih <em>Theme</em> yang lu inginkan, Lalu tekan “Select Theme”, Setelah itu kita akan diarahkan ke halaman editor untuk merubah isi dari halaman utama.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/github-page-edit-homepage-111fc61d5b0307f7126afb7cc9354d00-a007e.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 51.49812734082397%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Editor\"\n        title=\"Editor\"\n        src=\"/static/github-page-edit-homepage-111fc61d5b0307f7126afb7cc9354d00-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/github-page-edit-homepage-111fc61d5b0307f7126afb7cc9354d00-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/github-page-edit-homepage-111fc61d5b0307f7126afb7cc9354d00-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/github-page-edit-homepage-111fc61d5b0307f7126afb7cc9354d00-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/github-page-edit-homepage-111fc61d5b0307f7126afb7cc9354d00-526de.png 885w,\n/static/github-page-edit-homepage-111fc61d5b0307f7126afb7cc9354d00-a007e.png 1068w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Disini lu bisa edit halaman utama dari github pages lu. Gunakan Markdown untuk seluruh halaman di Github Pages.\nJika lu belum terbiasa dengan Markdown, Silakan ke <a href=\"https://help.github.com/articles/what-is-github-pages/\" title=\"Markdown Cheatsheet\">halaman ini</a> untuk tutorial Markdown.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/github-page-commit-1e266a2e337c78ce9424b3f2d6394313-4c473.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 36.95861405197306%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Your first Commit\"\n        title=\"Your first Commit\"\n        src=\"/static/github-page-commit-1e266a2e337c78ce9424b3f2d6394313-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/github-page-commit-1e266a2e337c78ce9424b3f2d6394313-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/github-page-commit-1e266a2e337c78ce9424b3f2d6394313-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/github-page-commit-1e266a2e337c78ce9424b3f2d6394313-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/github-page-commit-1e266a2e337c78ce9424b3f2d6394313-526de.png 885w,\n/static/github-page-commit-1e266a2e337c78ce9424b3f2d6394313-4c473.png 1039w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Nah, untuk setiap perubahan, kita harus commit perubahan tersebut</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/github-page-welcome-to-your-github-pages-534a678d7109cbbb0189e5282980ee01-2685f.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 66.46825396825396%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"Your first Github Pages\"\n        title=\"Your first Github Pages\"\n        src=\"/static/github-page-welcome-to-your-github-pages-534a678d7109cbbb0189e5282980ee01-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/github-page-welcome-to-your-github-pages-534a678d7109cbbb0189e5282980ee01-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/github-page-welcome-to-your-github-pages-534a678d7109cbbb0189e5282980ee01-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/github-page-welcome-to-your-github-pages-534a678d7109cbbb0189e5282980ee01-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/github-page-welcome-to-your-github-pages-534a678d7109cbbb0189e5282980ee01-526de.png 885w,\n/static/github-page-welcome-to-your-github-pages-534a678d7109cbbb0189e5282980ee01-2685f.png 1008w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Nah, kita sudah selesai membuat sebuah halaman <em>static</em> pada Github Page. Sekarang kita hanya tinggal membuka halaman tersebut dengan cara:</p>\n<p><em>nama-akun-github-lu.github.io/nama-repository</em></p>\n<p>Sebagai contoh hasil dari Tutorial diatas seperti <a href=\"https://ipoool.github.io/my-github-page\">disini</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Create a Github Pages","date":"November 12, 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/create-a-github-pages/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/hello-world/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Hello World"}},"next":null}}